1. Kupio sam *gorivo* za auto na pumpi. (I bought *fuel* for the car at the gas station.)
2. Nafte ima u izobilju, ali cene *goriva* ne prestaju da rastu. (There is an abundance of oil, but the *fuel* prices continue to rise.)
3. U Srbiji se sve više koristi *biogorivo* kao zamena za fosilna goriva. (In Serbia, *biofuel* is increasingly being used as a replacement for fossil fuels.)
4. *Gorivo* za grejanje kuće nam je ponestalo. (We ran out of *fuel* for heating the house.)
5. Nisam siguran koji *gorivni* filter je najbolji za ovaj tip motora. (I'm not sure which *fuel* filter is the best for this type of engine.)
6. Da bi se smanjila potrošnja *goriva*, važno je redovno održavati automobil. (In order to reduce *fuel* consumption, it is important to regularly maintain the car.)
7. Možete li mi preporučiti neku dobru *gorivnu* pumpu u blizini? (Can you recommend a good *fuel* pump nearby?)
8. Zbog smanjenja emisije štetnih gasova, neki proizvođači se prebacuju na *električna goriva*. (Due to the reduction of harmful gas emissions, some manufacturers are switching to *electric fuels*.)
9. Ovaj tip motora troši manje *goriva* u odnosu na prethodni model. (This type of engine consumes less *fuel* compared to the previous model.)
10. Da li znate koliko *goriva* je potrebno za put do Beograda? (Do you know how much *fuel* is needed for the trip to Belgrade?)